General.Name: Hsinjing Holding Co Ltd
General.Description: Hsinjing Holding Co., Ltd. engages in planning, designing, and installation of solar power generation systems in Taiwan. The company sells various types of solar panel modules; and invests in and sells solar power plants. It also holds a project site of approximately 50MW and a total of 205 power plants; and constructs and invests in solar photovoltaic systems. The company was founded in 1995 and is based in Zhubei, Taiwan.
